- `components/tldr-synergy-diagram.tsx` - Add interactions
- `components/tldr-tool-card.tsx` - Add ID for scroll target, highlight state
- `components/tldr-tool-grid.tsx` - Pass highlight callback

## Animation Details
- Use Framer Motion for node scale: `whileHover={{ scale: 1.1 }}`
- Connection glow: CSS filter or SVG gradient animation
- Scroll highlight: `ring-2 ring-violet-400` with fade out

## Accessibility
- Add `role="button"` and `tabIndex={0}` to nodes
- Support keyboard navigation (Tab between nodes, Enter to click)
- `aria-label` describing what click does
- Focus ring visible on keyboard focus

