- [ ] Maximum tilt angle ~5 degrees
- [ ] Smooth return animation on leave
- [ ] Subtle shine effect moves across
- [ ] Shadow responds to tilt direction
- [ ] Icon has parallax movement
- [ ] Disabled for reduced motion
- [ ] No performance impact (60fps)
